{"tid":1386173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【經濟制裁】美國國會：擴大經濟制裁侵犯香港人權的個體及組織，如拒發簽證","createTime":"2019-07-30T09:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T23:02:51.000Z","uid":14328,"like":1008,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":124,"replies":[{"pid":"bcb14f356ebaadc0e4a8e5d1333adb165d05d33c","tid":1386173,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/natdefense-990x520.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2Fnatdefense-990x520.jpg&h=62bef27f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年7月過去幾個星期，美國參眾兩院通過幾項2020年國防授權法 （National Defense Authorization Act）修訂案。其中的修訂，表明將會擴大針對包括中國在內多個國家的個人制裁。修訂案也特別提到了香港，並鼓勵美國制裁所有侵犯香港人人權和自由的個人或實體。<br />\n<br />\n參議院的法案，包括以香港為主的不具法律約束力的聲明。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/congress46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2Fcongress46.jpg&h=d656414a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「美國應該根據美國和國際法律，對所有侵犯香港人的基本人權和自由的個人和實體實施經濟制裁、拒發簽證及其他懲罰性的經濟措施。」<br />\n<br />\n法案原文： &ldquo;The United States should impose financial sanctions, visa bans, and other punitive economic measures against all individuals or entities violating the fundamental human rights and freedoms of the people of Hong Kong, consistent with United States and international law.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n國會將會解決參眾兩議院在修訂法案上的分歧部分，訂案應該在今年秋季表決及通過。"},{"pid":"f26a45dad989f9ddc72c6a52824aff5e94f33d39","tid":1386173,"uid":202876,"like":429,"dislike":3,"score":426,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:26:53.000Z","msg":"充公香港官員資產<br />\n美國fat fat<br />\nwin win相贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02090324bc9e61431d9b547703dcfb468b422f0e","tid":1386173,"uid":6528,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:27:38.000Z","msg":"全民8月5曰大罷工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選應要排最頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"1d80017df739024fc23cc2022b9ddb75b5496343","tid":1386173,"uid":6528,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:28:26.000Z","msg":"快啲過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65be551c8b06d1a344f708c9cdfcd01990d52db","tid":1386173,"uid":166405,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:28:56.000Z","msg":"出兵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a27adb1eb8b7728122867d913640e31e5c9863","tid":1386173,"uid":211525,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:30:54.000Z","msg":"但班官好多野都係英國"},{"pid":"b4129bd4cd27d2873bce1383142ec274d01bb8e6","tid":1386173,"uid":146737,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:34:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n自推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbGx8QX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfbGx8QX.jpg&h=d7da8d11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMXA6CM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMXA6CM.jpg&h=df77fed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jAzTbYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjAzTbYn.jpg&h=a3d7ff9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【文宣圖記錄版】反對逃犯條例修訂事件簿<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1376388/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1376388/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7168bfcf4451978908145337bd710b3f1035d9ac","tid":1386173,"uid":105590,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"重有加拿大 歐盟 英國 澳洲！<br />\n<br />\n唔可以慶祝住！"},{"pid":"5bb54c289e5797219a3185bdd34727e78a2db52b","tid":1386173,"uid":20696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:38:20.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快撚啲全球抵制添呀"},{"pid":"1b738339d8114fe262ea4ef455973c698a6cd2ce","tid":1386173,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b33cba477f52946aeb2ff2a577a8810074cd2a","tid":1386173,"uid":41245,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"quote":{"pid":"41a27adb1eb8b7728122867d913640e31e5c9863","tid":1386173,"uid":211525,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:30:54.000Z","msg":"但班官好多野都係英國"},"cit