9802daf70212fb8a451085c4c176f6c","tid":1386173,"uid":30290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:19:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要過就快d 過<br />\n唔好俾時間佢地走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"25a4361dd3a40607cddd5d1a327c926b06f6149b","tid":1386173,"uid":272592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bcb14f356ebaadc0e4a8e5d1333adb165d05d33c","tid":1386173,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/natdefense-990x520.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2Fnatdefense-990x520.jpg&h=62bef27f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年7月過去幾個星期，美國參眾兩院通過幾項2020年國防授權法 （National Defense Authorization Act）修訂案。其中的修訂，表明將會擴大針對包括中國在內多個國家的個人制裁。修訂案也特別提到了香港，並鼓勵美國制裁所有侵犯香港人人權和自由的個人或實體。<br />\n<br />\n參議院的法案，包括以香港為主的不具法律約束力的聲明。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/congress46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2Fcongress46.jpg&h=d656414a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「美國應該根據美國和國際法律，對所有侵犯香港人的基本人權和自由的個人和實體實施經濟制裁、拒發簽證及其他懲罰性的經濟措施。」<br />\n<br />\n法案原文： &ldquo;The United States should impose financial sanctions, visa bans, and other punitive economic measures against all individuals or entities violating the fundamental human rights and freedoms of the people of Hong Kong, consistent with United States and international law.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n國會將會解決參眾兩議院在修訂法案上的分歧部分，訂案應該在今年秋季表決及通過。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:19:41.000Z","msg":"仲要今年秋季先過得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n恨不得聽日就即刻過左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 